m=\"biblScope\">8.2.6</biblScope></bibl>, etc. ; <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">broil</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">fry</tr_> fish, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Fr.\">Fr.</a></title_> </bibl>l.c., <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0433.tlg001:17\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Crates Com.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">17</biblScope></bibl>, al.; <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">fry</tr_> an egg, <bibl n=\"http://www.trismegistos.org/text/63839\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ PLit.Lond.\">PLit.Lond.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">170</biblScope> </bibl> <date TEIform=\"date\">(i A. D.)</date>; <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">toast</tr_> cheese, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0458.tlg001:150:2\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eub.\">Eub.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">150.2</biblScope></bibl>.—Hence it appears that <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὀπτᾶν</foreign> was used of all kinds of <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">cooking by means of fire</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">dry heat,</tr_> opp. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἕψω</foreign> (boil in water), which never appears in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author></bibl>, whose heroes ate only roast meat, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κρέα δὲ μόνον ὤπτων, ἐπεὶ ἕψοντά γ᾽ οὐ πεποίηκεν αὐτῶν οὐδένα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0458.tlg001:120\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eub.\">Eub.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">120</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n74655.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\